------------For upstream-------------
UART Test
--------
Targeted HW platforms:
 Broalwell-U
 Baytrail-T

Purpose:
 Basic function tests like driver checking, device checking, baudrate setting .e.g

Driver source:
 ${Linux-kernel-tree}/drivers/tty/serial/8250/8250dw.c

Required Linux kernel config options:
 CONFIG_SERIAL_8250_DW

/!\ Use "make menuconfig" command to update Linux kernel config file and enable some potentially dependent options /!\


Hardware dependencies:
 N/A
